<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>AI Hunter Industry — AdSmart</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@400;600;700;900&family=Barlow:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #0A1628; --navy-mid: #0D1F3C; --navy-light: #142850;
    --azure: #4A9EE8; --orange: #F97316; --orange-dim: #C45A0E;
    --white: #FFFFFF; --gray-400: #8A9BB5;
  }
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body { background: var(--navy); color: var(--white); font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif; overflow-x: hidden; }
  body::before {
    content: ''; position: fixed; inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; opacity: 0.4;
  }
  .grid-bg {
    position: fixed; inset: 0;
    background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(74,158,232,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(74,158,232,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
  }
  section { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  /* ── LANG TOGGLE ── */
  .lang-toggle {
    display: flex; gap: 0; align-items: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(74,158,232,0.25);
  }
  .lang-btn {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 7px 14px; cursor: pointer; border: none;
    background: transparent; color: var(--gray-400);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .lang-btn.active { background: var(--azure); color: var(--white); }
  .lang-btn:hover:not(.active) { color: var(--white); }

  /* ── HIDDEN LANG CONTENT ── */
  [data-lang] { display: none; }
  .lang-es [data-lang="es"] { display: contents; }
  .lang-en [data-lang="en"] { display: contents; }
  /* For block elements that need display:block instead of contents */
  .lang-es [data-lang="es"].block-el { display: block; }
  .lang-en [data-lang="en"].block-el { display: block; }
  .lang-es [data-lang="es"].flex-el { display: flex; }
  .lang-en [data-lang="en"].flex-el { display: flex; }
  .lang-es [data-lang="es"].grid-el { display: grid; }
  .lang-en [data-lang="en"].grid-el { display: grid; }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    padding: 20px 8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(10,22,40,0.98) 0%, transparent 100%);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  }
  .logo-text {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 28px; color: var(--white); letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1;
  }
  .logo-dot { color: #F97316; margin-left: 2px; font-size: 22px; vertical-align: middle; }

  /* HERO */
  .hero { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; padding: 120px 8vw 80px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .hero::after { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -200px; right: -200px; width: 700px; height: 700px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(74,158,232,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%); pointer-events: none; }
  .hero-eyebrow { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 4px; color: var(--orange); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .hero-eyebrow::before { content: ''; width: 32px; height: 2px; background: var(--orange); }
  .hero-title { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: clamp(64px, 10vw, 120px); line-height: 0.9; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: -2px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .hero-title .line-azure { color: var(--azure); }
  .hero-title .line-orange { color: var(--orange); }
  .hero-sub { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: clamp(18px, 2.5vw, 26px); color: var(--gray-400); letter-spacing: 1px; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 48px; max-width: 640px; line-height: 1.4; }
  .hero-tags { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .tag { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 8px 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(74,158,232,0.3); color: var(--azure); background: rgba(74,158,232,0.06); }
  .tag.orange { border-color: rgba(249,115,22,0.3); color: var(--orange); background: rgba(249,115,22,0.06); }
  .hero-metric-row { display: flex; gap: 48px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .hero-metric { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
  .hero-metric-num { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 48px; color: var(--white); line-height: 1; }
  .hero-metric-num span { color: var(--orange); }
  .hero-metric-label { font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gray-400); }

  .divider { width: 100%; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(74,158,232,0.3), transparent); }

  /* SECTION COMMON */
  .section-label { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 5px; color: var(--orange); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 48px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
  .section-label::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: rgba(249,115,22,0.2); max-width: 200px; }
  .section-title { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px); text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 0.95; letter-spacing: -1px; }
  .section-title .accent { color: var(--azure); }

  /* PROBLEMA */
  .problem { padding: 100px 8vw; background: var(--navy-mid); }
  .problem-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2px; }
  .problem-item { padding: 36px; background: var(--navy); border-left: 3px solid transparent; transition: border-color 0.3s; }
  .problem-item:hover { border-left-color: var(--orange); }
  .problem-num { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 72px; color: rgba(249,115,22,0.1); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .problem-title { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 22px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .problem-text { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--gray-400); }

  /* SOLUCIÓN */
  .solution { padding: 100px 8vw; }
  .solution-top { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr; gap: 80px; align-items: end; }
  .solution-top-left .section-label { margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .solution-intro { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--gray-400); }
  .solution-metrics-bar { display: flex; align-items: center; margin: 56px 0 56px; background: var(--navy-mid); border: 1px solid rgba(74,158,232,0.12); }
  .sol-metric-bar { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 36px 24px; text-align: center; }
  .sol-metric-divider { width: 1px; height: 60px; background: rgba(74,158,232,0.15); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .sol-metric-num { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 52px; color: var(--white); line-height: 1; }
  .sol-metric-num span { color: var(--orange); font-size: 32px; }
  .sol-metric-label { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gray-400); }

  /* PILLARS */
  .pillars { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2px; }
  .pillar { background: var(--navy-mid); padding: 48px 36px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: transform 0.3s; }
  .pillar:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .pillar::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px; background: var(--azure); }
  .pillar:nth-child(2)::before { background: var(--orange); }
  .pillar:nth-child(3)::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--azure), var(--orange)); }
  .icon-line { width: 40px; height: 40px; margin-bottom: 24px; display: block; }
  .pillar-title { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 28px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--white); }
  .pillar-desc { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--gray-400); margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .pillar-features { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .pillar-features li { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-400); display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; line-height: 1.5; }
  .pillar-features li::before { content: '→'; color: var(--azure); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }

  /* TERRITORY */
  .territory { padding: 100px 8vw; background: var(--navy-mid); }
  .territory-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2px; margin-top: 60px; }
  .territory-card { background: var(--navy); padding: 48px 36px; position: relative; }
  .territory-card::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--azure), transparent); }
  .territory-icon { width: 32px; height: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; display: block; }
  .territory-zone { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 36px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .territory-sub { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: var(--orange); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .territory-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .territory-list li { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-400); padding-left: 16px; position: relative; line-height: 1.5; }
  .territory-list li::before { content: '·'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--azure); font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.1; }

  /* HOW */
  .how { padding: 100px 8vw; }
  .how-steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 2px; margin-top: 64px; position: relative; }
  .how-steps::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 32px; left: 0; right: 0; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--azure), var(--orange), transparent); z-index: 0; }
  .step { background: var(--navy-mid); padding: 40px 28px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .step-icon { width: 28px; height: 28px; margin-bottom: 20px; display: block; }
  .step-num { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 56px; line-height: 1; color: rgba(74,158,232,0.1); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .step-title { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 20px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .step-text { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--gray-400); }

  /* COMMERCIAL */
  .commercial { padding: 100px 8vw; background: var(--navy-mid); }
  .commercial-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2px; margin-top: 64px; }
  .commercial-card { background: var(--navy); padding: 56px 48px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .commercial-card.featured { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-light) 0%, #0D2140 100%); border: 1px solid rgba(74,158,232,0.2); }
  .commercial-card.featured::before { content: 'RECOMENDADO'; position: absolute; top: 24px; right: 24px; font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: var(--orange); background: rgba(249,115,22,0.1); padding: 4px 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.2); }
  .lang-en .commercial-card.featured::before { content: 'RECOMMENDED'; }
  .commercial-type { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 4px; color: var(--azure); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .commercial-price { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 64px; line-height: 1; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .commercial-price span { font-size: 28px; color: var(--gray-400); }
  .commercial-period { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-400); letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .commercial-includes { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .commercial-includes li { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-400); display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; line-height: 1.5; }
  .check-icon { width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
  .success-fee { background: rgba(249,115,22,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.2); padding: 20px 24px; margin-top: 8px; }
  .success-fee-label { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: var(--orange); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .success-fee-text { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-400); line-height: 1.6; }
  .paid-media-note { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(138,155,181,0.6); letter-spacing: 1px; margin-top: 12px; font-style: italic; }

  /* TECH */
  .tech { padding: 100px 8vw; }
  .tech-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 2px; margin-top: 64px; }
  .tech-item { background: var(--navy-mid); padding: 32px 28px; transition: background 0.3s; }
  .tech-item:hover { background: var(--navy-light); }
  .tech-icon { width: 32px; height: 32px; margin-bottom: 16px; display: block; }
  .tech-name { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .tech-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray-400); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* WHY */
  .why { padding: 100px 8vw; background: var(--navy-mid); }
  .why-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr; gap: 80px; align-items: start; margin-top: 64px; }
  .why-big-stat { text-align: center; padding: 48px; background: var(--navy); border: 1px solid rgba(74,158,232,0.15); position: sticky; top: 80px; }
  .why-stat-num { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 80px; line-height: 1; color: var(--azure); display: block; }
  .why-stat-label { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-400); letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 8px; display: block; }
  .why-items { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
  .why-item { background: var(--navy); padding: 32px 36px; display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: flex-start; border-left: 3px solid transparent; transition: border-color 0.3s; }
  .why-item:hover { border-left-color: var(--azure); }
  .why-item-icon { width: 28px; height: 28px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
  .why-item-title { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 20px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .why-item-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-400); line-height: 1.7; }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section { padding: 120px 8vw; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .cta-section::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); width: 800px; height: 400px; background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(249,115,22,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%); pointer-events: none; }
  .cta-title { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 88px); text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 0.9; letter-spacing: -1px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .cta-title .orange { color: var(--orange); }
  .cta-sub { font-size: 16px; color: var(--gray-400); max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 48px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .cta-btn { display: inline-block; font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; background: var(--orange); color: var(--white); padding: 20px 48px; text-decoration: none; position: relative; transition: all 0.3s; }
  .cta-btn::after { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: -3px; border: 1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.4); pointer-events: none; transition: inset 0.3s; }
  .cta-btn:hover { background: var(--orange-dim); }
  .cta-btn:hover::after { inset: -6px; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer { padding: 40px 8vw; border-top: 1px solid rgba(74,158,232,0.1); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .footer-tagline { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 4px; color: var(--gray-400); text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 6px; }
  .footer-contact { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-400); text-align: right; line-height: 1.8; }

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  @keyframes fadeInUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  .hero-eyebrow { animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease forwards; }
  .hero-title    { animation: fadeInUp 0.6s 0.1s ease both; }
  .hero-sub      { animation: fadeInUp 0.6s 0.2s ease both; }
  .hero-tags     { animation: fadeInUp 0.6s 0.3s ease both; }
  .hero-metric-row { animation: fadeInUp 0.6s 0.4s ease both; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .problem-grid, .pillars, .territory-grid, .how-steps, .commercial-grid, .tech-grid, .why-grid, .solution-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .solution-metrics-bar { flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .sol-metric-divider { display: none; }
    .why-big-stat { position: static; }
    nav { padding: 16px 5vw; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body class="lang-es">
<div class="grid-bg"></div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <span class="logo-text">AdSmart<span class="logo-dot">●</span></span>
  <div class="lang-toggle">
    <button class="lang-btn active" onclick="setLang('es')">ES</button>
    <button class="lang-btn" onclick="setLang('en')">EN</button>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-eyebrow">
    <span data-lang="es">AdSmart · Go-to-Market Intelligence · 2026</span>
    <span data-lang="en">AdSmart · Go-to-Market Intelligence · 2026</span>
  </div>
  <h1 class="hero-title">
    <span class="line-azure">AI HUNTER</span><br>
    <span>INDUSTRY</span><br>
    <span class="line-orange">O&G · MINERÍA</span>
  </h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">
    <span data-lang="es">Sistema inteligente de go-to-market para proveedores que quieren vender a Oil & Gas y Minería en Argentina. Presencia territorial real + Scoring Hunter AI + gestión activa de pipeline.</span>
    <span data-lang="en">Intelligent go-to-market system for suppliers looking to sell into Oil & Gas and Mining in Argentina. Real territorial presence + Scoring Hunter AI + active pipeline management.</span>
  </p>
  <div class="hero-tags">
    <span class="tag">Vaca Muerta</span>
    <span class="tag">San Juan</span>
    <span class="tag">Salta</span>
    <span class="tag orange">Scoring Hunter AI</span>
    <span class="tag orange"><span data-lang="es">Pipeline Inteligente</span><span data-lang="en">Intelligent Pipeline</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-metric-row">
    <div class="hero-metric">
      <span class="hero-metric-num">3<span>+</span></span>
      <span class="hero-metric-label"><span data-lang="es">Cuencas activas</span><span data-lang="en">Active basins</span></span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-metric">
      <span class="hero-metric-num">1.200<span>+</span></span>
      <span class="hero-metric-label"><span data-lang="es">Decisores mapeados</span><span data-lang="en">Mapped decision-makers</span></span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-metric">
      <span class="hero-metric-num">90<span>d</span></span>
      <span class="hero-metric-label"><span data-lang="es">Primeros resultados</span><span data-lang="en">First results</span></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- PROBLEMA -->
<section class="problem">
  <div class="section-label"><span data-lang="es">El Problema</span><span data-lang="en">The Problem</span></div>
  <div class="problem-grid">
    <div class="problem-item">
      <div class="problem-num">01</div>
      <div class="problem-title"><span data-lang="es">Sin presencia territorial</span><span data-lang="en">No territorial presence</span></div>
      <p class="problem-text"><span data-lang="es">Vaca Muerta, Salta y San Juan son mercados relacionales. Sin red local, los ciclos de venta se extienden 12–18 meses o directamente no ocurren.</span><span data-lang="en">Vaca Muerta, Salta and San Juan are relationship-driven markets. Without a local network, sales cycles stretch 12–18 months or simply never happen.</span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-item">
      <div class="problem-num">02</div>
      <div class="problem-title"><span data-lang="es">Inteligencia de mercado manual</span><span data-lang="en">Manual market intelligence</span></div>
      <p class="problem-text"><span data-lang="es">Las empresas no saben quién toma decisiones reales, cuándo se abren licitaciones ni qué proyectos están en etapa de aprobación de presupuesto.</span><span data-lang="en">Companies don't know who the real decision-makers are, when tenders open, or which projects are in budget approval stage.</span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-item">
      <div class="problem-num">03</div>
      <div class="problem-title"><span data-lang="es">Pipeline sin gestión sistemática</span><span data-lang="en">Unsystematic pipeline management</span></div>
      <p class="problem-text"><span data-lang="es">Los equipos de ventas trabajan con Excel y WhatsApp. Sin scoring ni seguimiento automatizado, las oportunidades se pierden por falta de timing.</span><span data-lang="en">Sales teams work with Excel and WhatsApp. Without scoring or automated tracking, opportunities are lost due to poor timing.</span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-item">
      <div class="problem-num">04</div>
      <div class="problem-title"><span data-lang="es">Costo de entrada prohibitivo</span><span data-lang="en">Prohibitive entry cost</span></div>
      <p class="problem-text"><span data-lang="es">Armar un equipo comercial propio en estas geografías cuesta entre USD 8.000–15.000/mes. La mayoría de los proveedores medianos no puede sostenerlo.</span><span data-lang="en">Building an in-house sales team in these geographies costs USD 8,000–15,000/month. Most mid-size suppliers can't sustain it.</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

