        <span data-lang="en">AI Hunter Industry combines real territorial presence across three basins with an AI-powered intelligence and scoring system. The Scoring Hunter AI automatically qualifies opportunities and the pipeline is actively managed by the AdSmart team — delivering in-house commercial performance at a fraction of the cost.</span>
